ANALYSIS
This bill requires schools to train at least 2 personnel in recognizing the symptoms of seizures
and the administration of seizure rescue medication in the event a seizure occurs at school. Parent
or guardian permission is required for the administration of seizure rescue medicine. The bill also
establishesaseizureeducationprograminpublicschools.
